dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Gregory Bryant. May I have your name please?
Hello, my name is Kelly Morgan.
Nice to meet you, Kelly. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, my policy number is seven eight four two six.
Thank you. Can you also confirm your date of birth for security purposes?
My date of birth is zero five one one, nineteen seventy-eight.
Great, thank you for verifying that information, Kelly. Is there anything specific you would like to inquire about or update on your policy today?
I would like to add a new vehicle to my policy, please.
Of course, Kelly. Let's proceed with adding the new vehicle to your policy. Thank you for choosing Old Stone Auto Insurance.
Thank you for your time, Kelly. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
